{"tid":2173011,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人農曆七月開始就失眠？","createTime":"2020-08-25T03:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T00:13:28.000Z","uid":259910,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"53b44135b35b942c735df3f73fcc4ff951d1e949","tid":2173011,"uid":259910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:50:06.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n平時完全冇失眠，一撻落床半個鐘入就瞓著<br />\n<br />\n依個禮拜生活習慣不變嘅情況下，失眠咗成個禮拜<br />\n明明身體好攰，但輾轉反側搵唔到一個可以完全放鬆嘅睡姿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時個腦好精神，不停諗埋啲無謂嘢<br />\n一直喺張床到由12點磨到4, 5點先勉強瞓到<br />\n然後第日起身冇精神同好燥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱同朋友傾起，原來佢依幾晚都瞓唔到<br />\n懷疑係咪鬼節搞到心緒不寧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf7daff8f79a3da22fce5c8e1ad6c0b86c1d6f7","tid":2173011,"uid":311002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"53b44135b35b942c735df3f73fcc4ff951d1e949","tid":2173011,"uid":259910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:50:06.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n平時完全冇失眠，一撻落床半個鐘入就瞓著<br />\n<br />\n依個禮拜生活習慣不變嘅情況下，失眠咗成個禮拜<br />\n明明身體好攰，但輾轉反側搵唔到一個可以完全放鬆嘅睡姿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時個腦好精神，不停諗埋啲無謂嘢<br />\n一直喺張床到由12點磨到4, 5點先勉強瞓到<br />\n然後第日起身冇精神同好燥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱同朋友傾起，原來佢依幾晚都瞓唔到<br />\n懷疑係咪鬼節搞到心緒不寧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T23:00:19.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d9ccd6543b9d91741e88643899e05df105a9dd","tid":2173011,"uid":288673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T23:16:27.000Z","msg